  "observations": [
    "Catalog is a hierarchical feed grouped by two-level Category (section → subsection)",
    "Kwork card composes preview image, title, price-from, seller rating, delivery time, and promo TOP badge",
    "Hover-preview reveals additional images + short description — lightweight detail peek without navigation",
    "Filters include price, deadline, seller rating, language, verification — filter surface mirrors seller-quality signals",
    "Sort offers algorithmic default plus freshness/price/rating — marketplace-style ranking",
    "Detail hero shows large gallery + title + price-from; markdown-formatted description with что-входит/не-входит/требуется",
    "KworkExtra is a first-class entity: multi-select checkboxes recompute total price live before order placement",
    "Seller mini-card surfaces response-time as trust signal",
    "Review list has secondary filters (with-photo, negative-only) — decision-support for buyers",
    "CTA 'Заказать за X ₽' embeds dynamic total — price is derived state from base + selected extras",
    "Kwork creation is a multi-step wizard with auto-save draft and moderation gate",
    "Moderation is an explicit state machine: draft → on_moderation → approved/rejected — ModerationDecision carries reason",
    "Orders tabbed by status: В работе / На проверке / Завершённые / Отменённые",
    "Order workflow has a bounded revision buffer (≤3) between delivered and completed — revision_requested is a first-class state, not a sub-field",
    "Due-date chip turns red when overdue — temporal witness surfaced in card",
    "Seller dashboard: stats (day/week/month), balance, conversion views→orders, per-kwork micro-stats",
    "Vacation toggle is a bulk operation over all active kworks — single switch on SellerProfile",
    "Order completion and cancellation are irreversible transitions (release of escrow, rating impact)",
    "Buyer and seller share the Orders screen but see role-scoped actions (buyer: request_revision, open_dispute; seller: deliver_order, mark_in_progress)"
  ]
}